        <p class="text-sm text-[var(--text-primary)] leading-relaxed"><strong>市场结构：</strong>下跌趋势，68,992-71,502 运行，成交量缩量。<br><strong>最关键水平：</strong>$69,893 — 前高与阻力重合。<br><strong>核心判断：</strong>等突破 69,893 失效或测试 70,941 阻力后再入场，不宜追空。</p>
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">入场参考</h3>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-3 mb-4">
        <div class="bg-[var(--bg-secondary)] rounded-lg p-4 text-center border border-white/5"><div class="text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)]">入场价</div><div class="text-lg font-bold text-white font-mono">69,893</div></div>
        <div class="bg-red-500/5 rounded-lg p-4 text-center border border-red-500/10"><div class="text-xs text-red-400">止损</div><div class="text-lg font-bold text-red-400 font-mono">70,941</div></div>
        <div class="bg-green-500/5 rounded-lg p-4 text-center border border-green-500/10"><div class="text-xs text-green-400">止盈1</div><div class="text-lg font-bold text-green-400 font-mono">68,992</div></div>
        <div class="bg-green-500/5 rounded-lg p-4 text-center border border-green-500/10"><div class="text-xs text-green-400">止盈2</div><div class="text-lg font-bold text-green-400 font-mono">69,951</div></div>
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">关键水平</h3>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-5 gap-2 mb-4">
        <div class="bg-[var(--bg-secondary)] rounded-lg p-3 text-center"><div class="text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)]">阻力2</div><div class="text-sm font-bold text-white font-mono">71,502</div></div>
        <div class="bg-[var(--bg-secondary)] rounded-lg p-3 text-center"><div class="text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)]">阻力1</div><div class="text-sm font-bold text-white font-mono">70,543</div></div>
        <div class="bg-primary/10 rounded-lg p-3 text-center border border-primary/30"><div class="text-xs text-primary">★中枢</div><div class="text-sm font-bold text-primary font-mono">69,893</div></div>
        <div class="bg-[var(--bg-secondary)] rounded-lg p-3 text-center"><div class="text-xs text-[var(--text-muted)]">支撑1</div><div class="text-sm font-bold text-white font-mono">68,992</div></div>
